snippet.title: The Continental: From the World of John Wick | Official Teaser | Peacock Original
snippet.description:
The Continental: From the World of John Wick is streaming September 2023 on Peacock: https://pck.tv/3m78jOD 

Synopsis: The three-part event will explore the origin behind the iconic hotel-for-assassins centerpiece of the John Wick universe through the eyes and actions of a young Winston Scott, as he’s dragged into the Hell-scape of 1970’s New York City to face a past he thought he’d left behind. Winston charts a deadly course through the hotel’s mysterious underworld in a harrowing attempt to seize the hotel where he will eventually take his future throne.

snippet.title: TIMBERWOLVES at LAKERS | #ATTPlayIn | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | April 11, 2023
snippet.description:
Never miss a moment with the latest news, trending stories and highlights to bring you closer to your favorite players and teams.
Download now: https://app.link.nba.com/APP22

Led by LeBron James’ 30 points, 10 rebounds, 6 assists, and 2 blocks, the Los Angeles Lakers defeated the Minnesota Timberwolves, 108-102. Anthony Davis added 24 points, 15 rebounds, 4 assists, and 3 blocks for the Lakers in the victory, while Karl-Anthony Towns tallied 24 points, 11 rebounds, 5 assists, and 3 blocks for the Timberwolves. With the victory, the Lakers have secured the No. 7 seed in the Western Conference of the 2023 NBA Playoffs where they will face the No. 2 seed Grizzlies, while the Timberwolves will play the winner of tomorrow’s New Orleans Pelicans-Oklahoma City Thunder Play-In Game, with the winner securing the No. 8 seed in the Western Conference of the 2023 NBA Playoffs.
